  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>Oe'd\n        und leer</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Cf. Tristan und Isolde, III, verse 24 [Eliot's note].\n        In act 3 of Tristan und Isolde, Tristan lies dying. He is\n        waiting for Isolde to come to him from Cornwall, but a\n        shepherd, appointed to watch for her sail, can only\n        report:</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font>link one</font></td>\n<td><a href=\"publication_data.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>link two</td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
